                                <condition>
                                    <p>The codex is not well preserved; in particular the first leaf
                                        has suffered and is now so dark that reading is difficult. A
                                        good deal of the leaves are mouldered or torn. The
                                        manuscript ends defectively.</p>
                                </condition>
                            </supportDesc>
