                        </additions>
                        <accMat>
                            <p> There is an AM-slip pasted in front of the codex. It reads: <q> fra
                                    Gudmundi Sigurdz sy <expan>n</expan> e a Alftanese, til eignar
                                        <date when="1704">1704</date> . </q>
                            </p>
                        </accMat>
